<module>
    <h>an diugh</h>
    <p><g>an diugh</g>
        <en>today</en> is an adverb.</p>

    <section id="forms">
        <h>forms</h>
        <p>Note that <g>an diugh</g> is usually spelled with a hyphen, as <g>an-diugh</g>, in
            post-1970s writing.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section id="uses-mod">
            <h>modifier</h>
            <p>Examples modifying a progressive verbal noun – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri agus Calum ag obair anns an achadh <m>an diugh</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary and Malcolm are working in the field today.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6–7</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl></p>
        </section>
    </section>




